struct_time = ref object
  tm_year*: int
  tm_mon*: range[1 .. 12]
  tm_mday*: MonthdayRange
  tm_hour*: HourRange
  tm_min*: MinuteRange
  tm_sec*: range[0 .. 61]
  tm_wday*: range[0 .. 6]
  tm_yday*: range[1 .. 366]
  tm_isdst*: int
  tm_zone*: string           ## .. warning:: curently is only "LOCAL" or "Etc/UTC"
  tm_gmtoff*: int
